            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> recover pins orphaned by the v1.0.185 pin-key escaping change</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> SettingsSync deletion branch compares against a fresh timestamp, not a stale one</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> stop SettingsPorterTests from wiping real production settings</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
