        <item>
            <title>1.0.192</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 10:17:51 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:channel>alpha</sparkle:channel>
            <sparkle:version>496</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.192</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> surface settings export write failures with an alert</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> seed both en-US and en-GB spellings of window-management titles</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> sanitize live AX title before comparing against stored title</li>
<li><strong>Improved:</strong> move system/third-party shortcut loading off the main actor</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> &quot;Keep Local Settings&quot; now also wins for keys unset locally</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> close two detachedScrapeTask races that let concurrent AX traversals run</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> quiz manual skip no longer double-advances</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> regenerate v1.0.185 alpha release notes with full changelog since v1.0.179</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> base alpha/beta release notes on the channel&#x27;s last published version</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
