            <sparkle:channel>alpha</sparkle:channel>
            <sparkle:version>479</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.185</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> escape | delimiter in favourite-shortcut pin keys</li>
<li><strong>Improved:</strong> fast-path exact-match ignore patterns instead of compiling an NSPredicate</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> don&#x27;t let a local settings deletion clobber a newer remote edit</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> derive live keypress key string from unshifted base character</li>
<li><strong>New:</strong> auto-generate Sparkle release notes in release.sh</li>
<li><strong>Fixed:</strong> remove dead string-catalog keys, localize settings-tab tooltips</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
